@Androbin
Thanks for the patch. Unfortunately I had issue with "tf.int64". TF would thrown an error if you wanted to minimize through tf.scatter_nd operation. 
Basically, computing a tf.gradient() for a computation graph that has a tf.scatter_nd op with tf.int64 indices throws an error.
